sql:
SELECT name, monthlyfee
FROM memberships
ORDER BY monthlyfee ASC;

SELECT AVG(monthlymaintenance) AS average_monthly_maintenance
FROM facilities
WHERE facid IN (0, 1);

external_knowledge:
- This question assumes that the booking date refers to the date the booking was made, not the date of the actual booking or event; 
- The query does not account for bookings that may have been cancelled or modified after they were made; 
- The results will not include facilities that did not receive any bookings in May 2023.
